The kingdom fell during a big war across the continent, and only [A] survived and went into hiding.
[B] has been haunting the castle ever since as a spectre, and over times she learned to control more and more of her powers; creating a fake kingdom for her to play in. Supressing the traumas from the war, she can still vividly imagine the huge armies that laid waste to her kingdom as is prepared to fight of any intruders.
